N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 107.2 - List of expense groups

State Regulations

Expenses reported in the operating expense classifications shall be allocated to the following expense groups: Investment expenses

Loss adjustment expenses

Acquisition, field supervision and collection expenses

Taxes, licenses and fees

General expenses
